yTime":"2017-03-26T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"黑色一點點係咩黎"},{"pid":"7d522ccd91ab79d8befa799a27f274d9e6702963","tid":174163,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:27:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑色一點點係咩黎</blockquote><br />\n黑椒"},{"pid":"d1f9760e0bf4f2422c1c811c22e442d13b42546c","tid":174163,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"原來中文叫希靈魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 芬蘭文叫Silli，原來係普通話譯音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 我都好鐘意食，係芬蘭果時朋友教我用rye bread + edam cheese + silli 整三文治食，搞到我係果到住果時日日早餐都咁整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我另一班朋友聽到就嚇到傻左，因為佢地話原來silli 係芬蘭好少人鐘意食，通常細路就嫌臭，老人家上左年紀先會鐘意"}]}